  "original_title": "\u0d9c\u0d82\u0da2\u0dcf \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0ddd 212 \u0d9a\u0dca \u0dc3\u0db8\u0d9c \u0d85\u0dba\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d9a\u0ddc\u0da7\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A person is arrested with 212 kilos of ganja",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "In a special search operation carried out by the Sri Lanka Navy in Puttalam Norochchole area this morning (06th), a suspect was caught with a van that was transporting about 212 kg of Kerala Ganja.",
        "Accordingly, the Sri Lanka Naval Ship Thambapanni, which belongs to the North West Naval Command, together with the Norochchole Police, inspected a suspicious van near the Karamba roadblock in Norochchole this morning. There, a suspect and the van were arrested along with a stock of 212 kg of Kerala ganja, which was being transported in ninety-seven parcels of ten bags.",
        "The gross street value of the Kerala ganja seized in this operation is believed to be over Rs 63 million.",
        "Furthermore, the arrested suspect was identified as a 32-year-old resident of Colombo 14, and the suspect and a 6-year-old boy in the van were taken to Norochchole Police Station for further legal proceedings along with the seized Kerala ganja stock and the van. Delivery was made."
      ],
